                    <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl">Your 3-day itinerary from
                        Bengaluru to the Jewel of Kedah is ready. Experience the perfect blend of strategic planning and
                        tropical serenity.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-base">
                        <button
                            class="px-8 py-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-xl font-label-sm text-label-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl active:scale-95 transition-all">
